        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="project-title">Predictive Modelling for Customer Acquisition</h1>
            <p class="project-subtitle">Optimized a bank's telemarketing campaign through advanced predictive analytics, resulting in 90% cost reduction and 2.5x increase in net profit.</p>
            
            <div class="project-meta">
                <!-- Date/Duration -->
                <div class="meta-item">
